::Zardus/Grimmler/The Galactors::

Zardus smiles, watching his missiles hit. He fires two more, all of
them heading at Rampage.

"The situation is fine, Najah," Zardus replies to Najah's
transmission, "Pick out a non-Maximal and slag them."

He sees Wheeljack and the other Alliance bots arrive and recieves
Wheeljack's transmission. "Yes. Do you have any weapon that might
cause a gestalt to decombine?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The two jets barrel roll, one shot hitting the Supernova/Slasys/Scrap
jet, but not doing any heavy damage. The jets fire their weapons again
at Surgital, two missiles and two charges flying out at the gestalt.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Grimler swirls in the air, one of the electric shots hitting him and
sending him flying backwards.




--- In nbwrpg@y..., "rAuq" <rauq@t...> wrote:
> OOC: is Kluster in front of the CF?
> 
> ::Rippersnapper/Razorclaw/Rampage/Divebomb::
> 
> Rippersnapper takes another rocket in the chest blasting him 
> backwards, and putting another dent in his armour. "NO MORE 
> ROCKETS," he yells, getting angry. He gets up, and starts rushing 
> Kluster, firing three shots from his cyclone gun, at the bot.
> 
> Razorclaw shoots six concussion blasts at the large jet, continuing 
> upward.
> 
> Rampage gets hit by the energy draining missiles, he can feel the 
> power levels dropping, but he manages to get out of the field, and 
> continues upward. He shoots his electricity rifle four times through 
> the missiles sent by Grimmler, destroying them. The shots 
> continue on at Grimmler.
> 
> Divebomb fires three blasts from his particle rifle, at the combined 
> jets.
